      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a super reliable ride that\u2019s ready for your next road trip? I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car, and it\u2019s honestly in great shape! It\u2019s been well-loved and looked after, so you can expect a smooth drive and a clean interior. It\u2019s perfect for someone who wants a quality vehicle without the brand-new price tag. Come take it for a spin\u2014I think you\u2019re going to love it!",
