    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E92 M3 is a purist's delight, powered by the high-revving S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8 featuring eight individual throttle bodies and an 8,400 RPM redline. The 7-speed M-DCT dual-clutch transmission provides instantaneous gear changes, paired with a variable M differential lock for superior lateral traction. Equipped with Electronic Damper Control (EDC), the chassis remains composed through high-load cornering. Recent preventative maintenance includes rod bearing inspection and a throttle actuator refresh, ensuring the valvetrain and VANOS system perform to factory specifications. A mechanically robust example with sharp turn-in and a linear power band.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
