      "description": "Presented for your consideration is a meticulously maintained vehicle that exemplifies reliable performance and sophisticated design. This unit has undergone a comprehensive multi-point inspection to ensure it meets our rigorous standards for mechanical integrity and aesthetic appeal. Offering a balanced blend of comfort and capability, it represents an exceptional acquisition for the discerning driver seeking a dependable, high-quality pre-owned option.",
      "price": 34800.0,
